    <item>
      <title>随着法律费用的增加，特朗普在竞选筹款方面落后于拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/trump-trails-biden-on-campaign-fundraising-as-legal-fees-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的政治运作在 2 月份额外花费了 560 万美元的法律费用，削弱了这位共和党推定提名人的政治筹款活动，而该筹款活动继续落后于他的民主党对手的现金筹集。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/trump-trails-biden-on-campaign-fundraising-as-legal-fees-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:07:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“政治地震”震撼了越南的继承之战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/-political-earthquake-shakes-up-succession-battle-in-vietnam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南可能没有出现许多民主国家分裂的两极分化的选举，但在短短一年多的时间里第二位总统的下台表明，一党制国家内部的闭门权力斗争也可能同样残酷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/-political-earthquake-shakes-up-succession-battle-in-vietnam</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 01:52:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在印度印地语中心地带，农民的困境并没有阻碍莫迪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-03-21/farmers-in-rural-india-hold-key-to-modi-winning-third-term-as-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执政的印度人民党日益根深蒂固的受欢迎程度在很大程度上依赖于农村地区——但许多人只看到该党执政十年来所带来的好处有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-03-21/farmers-in-rural-india-hold-key-to-modi-winning-third-term-as-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 01:00:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙中右翼领导人在选举中以微弱优势获胜后被任命为总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/portugal-s-center-right-leader-named-prime-minister-after-narrow-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙中右翼领导人路易斯·黑山在其联盟本月以微弱优势赢得选举后被任命为总理，这给他带来了试图以少数派政府执政的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/portugal-s-center-right-leader-named-prime-minister-after-narrow-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:26:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
